= stylesheet_link_tag    "detail_pages"

#weekly-ad  
  %section#feature-header
    %h1
      Shopping List
    %p
      Capture shopper attention with a Weekly Ad designed for the digital world
  
  %section#body-text  
    .row-fluid
      .span8
        %h2
          Overview
        %ul
          %li
            Shoppers who access weekly ads online spend more in store - Nielson
          %li
            The weekly ad is the most popular feature on grocery websites
          %li
            93% of retailers display their weekly ad online, so how are you differentiating yours?

        %p
          A retailer's digital presence isn't complete without a comprehensive, interactive shopping list. Quick list creation with weekly ad items, recipes, digital coupons and easy entry helps consumers shop quickly and be confident that they purchased everything they need.

        %h2
          Shopping List Features
          
        %ul.feature-detail
          %li
            %span.icon-list.icon
            One list with all important entries from digital circular, recipes, coupons
          %li
            %span.icon-mobile.icon
            Create on website or mobile
          %li
            %span.icon-interface.icon
            Same data on all digital media
          %li
            %span.icon-healthy.icon
            Organized by department for easy shopping
          %li
            %span.icon-tag.icon
            Sale prices, expiration date and purchase requirements included
          %li
            %span.icon-tree.icon
            Print version, mobile and email
          %li
            %span.icon-cart.icon
            Mobile features tailored for in-store experience, "Groceries in Cart" tracking
      .span4
        .image-center
          = image_tag "index/shopping-list.png"
        %div.center-button
          %a.btn{:href => 'index#contact-us'} Curious? Contact Us For More Info